    public class AddFormJDialog
extends javax.swing.JDialog
    AddFormJDialog.java AddFormJDialog is called when the user selects to add a new golfer. The dialog allows the user to input first name, last name, email, phone number, and golfer rating. Prior to leaving any field they are validated by the Validation class so user must input correct parameters before being able to add new golfer. Once all parameters are met and user selects to add golfer this form disposes itself.
